{"tid":1125350,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解marvel入面人類同地球都咁屈機","createTime":"2019-04-25T15:42:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T05:16:03.000Z","uid":36134,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c29d40e0d83b93f5a0de12f54c16f74b762ac6","tid":1125350,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:42:15.000Z","msg":"明明係宇宙入面<br />\n地球係各方面都屬於好落後既地區<br />\n但好多次危機人類同地球都會成為拯救宇宙既關鍵<br />\n宇宙咁撚大 屈機過地球既星球又咁多<br />\n地球科技又落後 但居然有咁多超能力者 <br />\nD科技戰力又會咁癲<br />\n又有咁多屈機變種人 <br />\n仲有d神怪 魔法師又盛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個marvel宇宙先進過地球我諗閒閒地<br />\n無幾萬 都有幾百個掛<br />\n其他先進過地球既星際文明到底有咩用<br />\n有無人可以解釋到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d7af405784484a3e65e7a76673ce4ed004688a","tid":1125350,"uid":237015,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:47:38.000Z","msg":"是但啦<br />\n唔通整套一大班蟲樣/五顏六色嘅外星人救宇宙你會睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5811e0b2fb6e81b2c1d48e2bc6d58691939d4a85","tid":1125350,"uid":6195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為啲作者全部都係地球人囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fce752bef3b840522cde556c2bbcd16df0b2fe","tid":1125350,"uid":1330,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:49:45.000Z","msg":"因為marvel係虛構 只係漫畫 電影嚟<br />\n而呢套漫畫係地球人畫 唔係火星人畫"},{"pid":"515823e02703d967ffd6c55441403313beffe702","tid":1125350,"uid":206895,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:50:16.000Z","msg":"因為作者係地球人，完，情況就好似點解英文變咗宇宙流通語言"},{"pid":"08be29ba6e38a00981a5e11c73035287fe9b4fda","tid":1125350,"uid":16061,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T15:50:57.000Z","msg":"其他星球打緊比thanos勁幾百倍嘅boss又要同你交代咩"},{"pid":"9091ab486b121e6ad1e2f23fb014